  "text": "Instead of building one powerful subgraph as did in [CITATION_1] , our basic idea is to establish a path system such that there exist a few segments in each path that can be replaced by paths with difference residue. We prove a number theoretical result on sumsets of integers to ensure the desired path system exists.",
